0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"泛民：裸辭？不了&hellip;"},{"pid":"33844a34d98acc70975798655c5a6456c1935ffc","tid":321673,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等埋 Court of Final Appeal 先啦</blockquote><br />\n而家中共想過23條就過 想改議事規則就改到<br />\n再留係議會跟本無作用<br />\n全部總辭搞大件寧好過</blockquote><br />\n如果立會停止運作，23條一定過唔到。"},{"pid":"55fab466f2cf583d99333e9d00c2b3cf06f00c91","tid":321673,"uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泛民：裸辭？不了&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">泛民裸辭喇，令立會停止運作，難道你地份工，重要得過23條立法？</span></span>"},{"pid":"82df67b28aebf5cea86bb1dcdeb371558b05a9f2","tid":321673,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等埋 Court of Final Appeal 先啦</blockquote><br />\n而家中共想過23條就過 想改議事規則就改到<br />\n再留係議會跟本無作用<br />\n全部總辭搞大件寧好過</blockquote><br />\n如果立會停止運作，23條一定過唔到。</blockquote><br />\n30個辭職仲有40個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家留係議會都係眼白白睇各種議案通過<br />\n不過總辭好過"},{"pid":"a886ef5dc8ee0bedf88f6e628576138983078f57","tid":321673,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>泛民：裸辭？不了&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">泛民裸辭喇，令立會停止運作，難道你地份工，重要得過23條立法？</span></span></blockquote><br />\n總辭之後點解會停止運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fddbc2d9df94865b7c4dab55706a6e7ff64b9d","tid":321673,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"係抗爭"},{"pid":"af0eb4a649bd3c51f14caabb29fb0572b74b0ddd","tid":321673,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泛民：裸辭？不了&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">泛民裸辭喇，令立會停止運作，難道你地份工，重要得過23條立法？</span></span></blockquote><br />\n總辭之後點解會停止運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇足夠議員，立法會會停止運作。"},{"pid":"e74931ea6bdccc4d034002fe71514fed43b8019d","tid":321673,"uid":108101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"太悲觀"},{"pid":"8faad828ac48bdfb5a78ed5ac864db29f90145b8","tid":321673,"uid":40839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泛民：裸辭？不了&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">泛民裸辭喇，令立會停止運作，難道你地份工，重要得過23條立法？</span></span></blockquote><br />\n總辭之後點解會停止運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇足夠議員，立法會會停止運作。</blockquote><br />\n40個照run架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過而家泛民已經失去制衡作用<br />\n總辭攬炒好過"},{"pid":"dd9af5c7b87d741742f239e5f451bceb2c2fdcc1","tid":321673,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"泛民：要番工，不了"},{"pid":"35b4808006d81fe6ece92f618f84fb3617f73704","tid":321673,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等埋 Court of Final Appeal 先啦</blockquote><br />\n而家中共想過23條就過 想改議事規則就改到<br />\n再留係議會跟本無作用<br />\n全部總辭搞大件寧好過</blockquote><br />\n23條只要過半<br />\n其實佢想硬推幾時都過得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebcfdcefe19f808a329399395c3194059c2a931","tid":321673,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>等埋 Court of Final Appeal 先啦</blockquote><br />\n而家中共想過23條就過 想改議事規則就改到<br />\n再留係議會跟本無作用<br />\n全部總辭搞大件